ControllerContext.CtxRcvdMsgCalls
public class ReceivedMessageByTypeCalls
extends java.lang.Object

Retained list of received SBOFMessagePB call-backs.

Provides implementation for ControllerContext addReceiveMessageType() and addReceiveMessageFilter() and related calls.
